    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## AI Data Coach\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to get feedback at any point in your project.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Do This:**\r\n\r\n1. Ask AI Chat to help with one of these:\r\n   - Refine your data question\r\n   - Interpret your graph\r\n   - Turn bullet points into a paragraph \r\n   - Clean a messy data entry\r\n2. Review its suggestion.  \r\n3. Decide how you’ll use the feedback in your project.  \r\n\r\n::: details [**Here's how to download your dataset as a PDF**]\r\n![](https://images.code.org/4997fb44a36f4e902f3ce8fe5808605f-image-1744828202871.29.44 PM.png)\r\n:::\r\n\r\n",
